<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.9">
<l>virumpip pakavaraik kāṇil viyaliṭa muṇṭāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>karumperu mēkaṅkaḷ kāṇiṟ kaṇṇaṉ ṉeṉṟēṟap paṟakkum</l>
<l>perumpula vānirai kāṇil pirāṉuḷa ṉeṉṟupiṉ cellu</l>
<l>marumpeṟal peṇṇiṉai māyō ṉalaṟṟi yayarppikkiṉ ṟāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When she longingly sees sages she says “he ate the vast area”,</l>
<l>when she sees black large clouds she flies high up, saying “Kaṇṇaṉ”,</l>
<l>when she sees the cow herd in the big field she goes after [it], saying “he is the lord”.</l>
<l>[My] girl difficult to obtain, incessantly the Dark one makes [her] forget.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
